TextEng: Pleased to meet you, Chandra.
Hello, Chandra. Me name be <FullName>.
I think I'll be going now.
Sorry, you must have me confused with someone else.
Text: 미안하지만, 나를 다른 사람으로 착각한 것 같아.

TextEng: Greetings, Chandra. My name is <FullName>.
Me name be <FullName>.
I think I'll be going now.
Me go now.
Me go now.
Me think you not know me. You thinking of some other one.
Text: 나 너 나 몰라. 너 다른 사람 생각하는 거야.

TextEng: Why do you want to meet Lady Aribeth so badly?
Text: 왜 아리베스 경을 그렇게 만나고 싶어?

TextEng: How's your training going, Chandra?
Can I ask you some questions?
Why you want meet Aribeth so bad?
Text: 너 왜 아리베스 그렇게 만나고 싶어?

TextEng: How you training going, Chandra?
Me want ask you some questions.
What can you tell me about the plague?
Text: 역병에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Have you heard those rumors about a cure for the plague?
How do you like training here at the Academy?
What you know 'bout plague?
You hear stuff 'bout cure for plague?
You like training at Academy?
Your lessons sound difficult. How are you holding up?
Text: 네 수업이 어려워 보이네. 어떻게 버티고 있어?

TextEng: You work sound hard. You hold up good still?
Text: 너 일 힘들게 들려. 너 괜찮아?

TextEng: I wouldn't call that dream foolish.
Me not think you dream silly.
Text: 나 너 꿈 바보같다고 생각 안 해.

TextEng: Don't worry, I still want to get together.
Text: 걱정 마, 나 아직도 만나고 싶어.

TextEng: You no worry, me still want see you later.
Text: 너 걱정 마, 나 아직도 나중에 보고 싶어.

TextEng: Actually, I can't get together with you later after all.
Text: 사실, 나중에 같이 있을 수 없을 것 같아.

TextEng: Me sorry. Me no can see you later.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 나중에 못 봐.

TextEng: I came to the Academy to learn, Chandra, not to get hit on by desperate, lonely sorceresses.
Text: 난 배우러 사관학교에 왔지, 필사적이고 외로운 요술사한테 작업 당하러 온 게 아니야, 찬드라.

TextEng: Normally I object to flattery, but only a fool dismisses compliments from a beautiful woman.
Text: 평소엔 아첨을 싫어하지만, 아름다운 여성의 칭찬을 무시하는 건 바보짓이지.

TextEng: No offense, but I'm not interested.
Text: 기분 나쁘게 받아들이진 말고, 관심 없어.

TextEng: Me like nice words from pretty woman.
Text: 나 예쁜 여자가 좋은 말 하는 거 좋아.

TextEng: Me here for training! Me not care 'bout this stuff!
Text: 나 여기 훈련하러 왔어! 나 이런 거 관심 없어!

TextEng: You be sad, ugly woman. Me no want be friend with you!
Text: 너 슬프고 못생긴 여자야. 나 너랑 친구 하기 싫어!

TextEng: Actually I'm not seeing anyone right now.
Text: 사실 지금 아무도 만나고 있지 않아.

TextEng: That's really none of your business, Chandra.
Text: 그건 네가 상관할 일이 아니야, 찬드라.

TextEng: Me not seeing anyone right now.
That not be none of you business, Chandra!
I'd like that, Chandra.
Sorry, but I'm not interested.
Uh... I'm already going with somebody. Sorry, Chandra.
Text: 어... 나 이미 누군가랑 가기로 했어. 미안해, 찬드라.

TextEng: Me like that, Chandra.
Me not interested. Sorry.
Uh... me got date already. Sorry, Chandra.
Text: 어... 나 이미 약속 있어. 미안해, 찬드라.
